ARCHITECTURE.md
     1вҶ’# Architecture
     3вҶ’> Document is a work in progress!
     4вҶ’
     5вҶ’вҢҳK is born from a simple constraint: can you write a combobox with filtering and sorting using the [compound component](https://kentcdodds.com/blog/compound-components-with-react-hooks) approach? We didn't want to render items manually from an array:
     6вҶ’
     7вҶ’```tsx
     8вҶ’// No
     9вҶ’<>
    10вҶ’  {items.map((item) => {
    11вҶ’    return <div>{item}</div>
    12вҶ’  })}
    13вҶ’</>
    14вҶ’```
    15вҶ’
      вҶ’вҖҰ
